column5: We are looking for a sales rep for the Oshawa/Whitby area. Salary + bonuses+ expenses.  Must enjoy meeting people, be able to work with minimul supervision, and be interested in making a good living.  The job is calling on businesses and food service accounts, some leads provided and some cold calling required.  You'd be representing a well known, well established and highly respected company.  If you are interested let me know ASAP. I don't get to make the final decision but I can make sure your resume gets to the top of the pile because I will be your immediate supervisor.  [emailÂ protected]  or call me if you have any questions Home 705-328-0577
